

### 🔐 **User Levels & Permissions**

| **Role** | **PIN** | **Name** | **Permissions** |
|----------|---------|----------|-----------------|
| **👑 Admin** | `0000` | Alex Admin | **ALL PERMISSIONS** - Can process refunds, modify products, manage employees, view reports, modify settings, access admin |
| **📊 Manager** | `1234` | John Manager | **LIMITED ADMIN** - Can process refunds, modify products, view reports, access admin. **Cannot** manage employees or settings |
| **💼 Employee** | `5678` | Sarah Johnson | **POS ONLY** - No admin permissions, limited to POS operations |
| **💼 Employee** | `9999` | Mike Smith | **POS ONLY** - No admin permissions, limited to POS operations |


**Test with different PIN codes:**

1. **Admin Access (PIN: `0000`)**:
   - ✅ Can access ALL features
   - ✅ Can process refunds
   - ✅ Can modify all filters
   - ✅ Full admin control

2. **Manager Access (PIN: `1234`)**:
   - ✅ Can process refunds
   - ✅ Can view/filter transactions
   - ❌ Cannot manage employees
   - ❌ Cannot modify system settings

3. **Employee Access (PIN: `5678` or `9999`)**:
   - ❌ Cannot access admin transactions page
   - ❌ Blocked from all admin functions
   - ✅ Can use POS interface only